] has Advantage on Strength checks and Strength saving throws.\n- **Duration.** The rage lasts for 10 min and ends if [MON] gains the incapacitated condition."},{"name":"Dash","desc":"[MON] can take the _Dash_ action as a bonus action."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Unyielding","desc":"While [MON] is moving, if he is targeted by at attack or subjected to an effect that would move him, knock him prone, or both, he can use his reaction to gain +2 AC and neither be moved nor knocked prone."}],"legendaries":[{"name":"Gore Charge","desc":"[MON] charges up to 30 feet in a straight line and makes one **Gore** attack."},{"name":"Infernal Benediction(Costs 2 Actions)","desc":"[MON] calls upon Bel to empower his allies. All creatures friendly to [MON] that can hear him add [1D8] fire damage to their attacks until the beginning of [MON]’s next turn."},{"name":"Flames of Dominion (Costs 3 Actions)","desc":"[MON] casts _Fireball_ at level 3 with a DC of 16. [MON] can select up to 3 creatures to not be succeed the saving throw and take no damage."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"fire","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"(piercing, bludgeoning, slashing while Raging)","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Giant","speaks":true},{"name":"Infernal","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Ranbur","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}